== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 9 Gashyantare 1976 i Johannesburg, muri [[Afurika y'Epfo.]] Ise Richard Moss ni umwongereza-Afurika yepfo aho sekuru yari isake. Nyina Veronica Salt yari afite amateka ya Irilande. Kubwibyo, Colin yavutse afite imico ivanze yabongereza, Irilande, Abadage na Afrika yepfo. Yatsinze ukulele na saxofone ikina.

Yashakanye n'umuyobozi wa Afrika yepfo, Tamarin Kaplan. Ubukwe bwizihijwe muri 2014 muri Stellenbosch .

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye umwuga we wo gukina nkumunyarwenya uhagaze kuri Afrika yepfo yihagararaho. Yakomeje gukora urwenya hagati yimyidagaduro yo gukina imyaka myinshi. Nyuma yaje kurangiza impamyabumenyi yikinamico muri kaminuza ya Kwazulu-Natal mu 1996. Yatangiye gukina binyuze mu bitaramo bimwe na bimwe nka ''Fat Pig'' na ''My Zinc Bed'' . Mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 90, yakinnye buri gihe na gahunda ye ya stage nk'umunyarwenya muri Afurika y'Epfo ndetse no mu minsi mikuru itandukanye yo gusetsa. a. no mu Bwongereza na Irilande. Muyindi nzira yumwuga we, Moss yakomeje gukora nkurwenya. Kuva mu 2003 umuyobozi w'itsinda risetsa 'Comedy All Stars Cape Town' muri Cape Town. Mu mwaka wa 2010, yakoze porogaramu ye yo gusetsa muri Stand Up Comedy Club mu mujyi wa New York.

Mu 1998, yerekanwe bwa mbere kuri tereviziyo na televiziyo ''Isidingo'' aho yakinnye nka 'Stewart Buller'. Yagaragaye muri uruhererekane kuva 1999 kugeza 2001 akunzwe cyane. Hanyuma yagiye i Cape Town, akora akazi ko gutanga ibiganiro kuri tereviziyo zitandukanye, harimo na TV ''Life City'' 2001. Mu 2002, yabaye umunyamakuru wa stunt show ''Fear Factor'' . Muri 2003, 2005 na 2007 yafashe icyemezo cyo kwerekana imiziki nimpano ya 'Idols South Africa' in season 3 <ref name="news24">https://www.news24.com/you/celebs/where-is-colin-moss-now-20190212</ref>

Mu 2005, Moss yagize ijyana gabo uruhare mu ikinamico y'Epfo ''Number 10.'' Uyu yakinnye muri Afurika yepfo Horror ''Cryptid'' mu 2006 yafashe umwanya wa Mioss Dan Huevelman. Mu 2007, yinjiye muri filime yo gusetsa yo muri Afurika yepfo ''Big Fellas'' akina kimwe mu bintu bibiri by'ingenzi; 'umusore Jake Holmes'. Muri uwo mwaka, yakinnye muri filime ''yihishe'' y'Abongereza n'Afurika y'Epfo aho yakinnye nka 'Officer De Witt'. Muri 2008, yagize uruhare runini nka 'John' muri comediyo y'Ubutaliyani n'Abafaransa ''Ex'' . Hanyuma yakinnye umukinnyi wa firime hamwe numunyamurwango 'Dexter "Dex" Simms' muri firime iteye ubwoba ''Surviving Evil'' muri 2009. 

Bitewe nuburengerazuba bwe, yahisemo gukina amafilime mpuzamahanga nka: 'Ofisiye DeWitt' mu ikinamico ''The World Unseen'' . Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mpuzamahanga. Nyuma yaje kugira uruhare runini muri film ''Surviving Evil'' aho yakinnye na Billy Zane. Yakinnye kandi nka 'Max' mu guhuza BBC na DH Lawrence's ''Women in Love'' . Moss yakinnye nka 'Kevin Fuller' muri filime ''Momentum ari'' kumwe na James Purefoy na Morgan Freeman .

Muri Werurwe 2014, yagaragaye muri filime ya televiziyo ya ZDF ''Elly Beinhorn'' . Muri 2015, yimukiye mu mujyi wa New York ahita asinywa na The Talent House. Nyuma yibyo, yakinnye inshuro nyinshi 'Justin Boden' kuri Marvel yakunzwe cyane na Netflix, ''Jessica Jones'' . Hanyuma yakinnye nka 'Anthony' muri ''Black Mirror'' ya Netflix ndetse no muri seriveri ya David Simon yitwa ''Deuce'' . Hagati aho, yagize uruhare runini muri filime ''Hanyuma Yaje Nawe'' hamwe n 'uruhare rwa' Drew Conrad 'muri filime ''Noheri mu gasozi'' . 

